msgctxt "Addon Summary"
msgid "GCE - Vectrex (vecx)"
msgstr "GCE - Vectrex (vecx)"

msgctxt "Addon Description"
msgid "Vecx is a Vectrex video game system emulator. It can run most Vectrex software."
msgstr "Vecx je emulátor herního systému Vectrex. Dokáže spustit většinu softwaru pro Vectrex."

